{"tid":723290,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"如果前度知錯，會唔會比多一次機會佢？","createTime":"2018-06-30T09:21:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T09:35:31.000Z","uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8656b8932c139836cba7d676e8c4cc568a29cf2f","tid":723290,"uid":102240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:21:04.000Z","msg":"我同佢大約五月分開，事源係當初太快係埋一齊，未了解清楚對方......同佢一齊左差唔多一個月到佢D壞習慣開始浮上面，行街睇戲返深圳食野都要AA，有時出街天氣熱我扮下黑面佢又唔識tum我，死唔認低威，岩岩分開果陣差唔多一齊左幾星期，當時我嬲到以後都唔想見到佢，就Block哂佢所有野，佢都有不停去搵我想道歉認錯，話佢已經改好哂啲問題，同埋去做好多野想氹返我，但當時我覺得佢係得把口，咁短時間邊有可能改到，所以都好決絕同佢講唔會一齊返，之後佢就失左蹤，最近過左差唔多一個月，佢搵返我，同我傾左輪計，我覺得佢真係大個仔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想同佢一齊返，但唔知應該點開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a35222d2f40e3932f8fee6a877f553c022cdad6","tid":723290,"uid":185103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:23:36.000Z","msg":"你真係願意比多次機會我？<br />\n我改過架啦，以前扑1秒就射<br />\n我依家20幾秒先射架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c0f8c8ed41f6d009ed03f87aa55e94a6c3147e","tid":723290,"uid":38428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:26:43.000Z","msg":"你掛住比佢扑嗰陣咋掛？"},{"pid":"64eb5b2b80f3d8a0bf97ac864d850d5f6294df2d","tid":723290,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:27:53.000Z","msg":"公廁想洗底？"},{"pid":"d9ef1eed07c7e87186a99708823a8d152f98edeb","tid":723290,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac7671f243a4cee37c79813ac79730c13e2bd28","tid":723290,"uid":8253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"天氣熱就黑面 不了<img src=